OL,3,CTwo more men charged following crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed grandmother in her 70s
OL,6,FGillian Livingstone, a grandmother
OL,7,Ffrom Cleator Moor, was killed after
OL,8,Fshe and her grandchild were struck by
OL,9,Fa motorbike whilst crossing the road.
OL,11,FThe fatal collision took place on
OL,12,FEnnderdale Road in Cleator Moor at
OL,13,F4.25pm, on 26 May.
OL,15,FThe 75-year-old was pronounced dead at
OL,16,Fthe scene and her grandchild was taken
OL,17,Fto hospital having suffered a serious
OL,18,Fhead injury.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
