OL,3,CTwo more men charged following crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed grandmother in her 70s
OL,6,FCumbria Police initially arrested
OL,7,Fthree men, all from West Cumbria and
OL,8,Fall in their 20s, following the crash.
OL,10,FOfficers investigating the incident
OL,11,Fhave now charged two men overnight (9
OL,12,FJuly) with causing death by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving.
OL,15,F22-year-old Workington man, Kieran
OL,16,FJoseph Yorke, has previously been
OL,17,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving.
OL,20,FThe other two men were bailed whilst
OL,21,Finvestigations continued.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
