CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783961288
OL,3,CTwo more men charged following crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed grandmother in her 70s
OL,6,FOvernight, 22-year-old Shaun Rafferty
OL,7,Fof Seaton and 23-year-old Stefan Young
OL,8,Fof Whitehaven, have also been charged.
OL,10,FThey were bailed and will attend
OL,11,FWorkington Magistrates' Court on 3
OL,12,FAugust 2026.
OL,14,FIn June, an inquest into Mrs
OL,15,FLivingstone's death was opened and
OL,16,Fthen suspended due to the ongoing
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
