OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783961288
OL,3,CTwo more men charged following crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed grandmother in her 70s
OL,6,FCumbria Coroner's Court, sitting in
OL,7,FWorkington, heard on Tuesday 16 June
OL,8,Fhow the 75-year-old lost her life
OL,9,Fafter she suffered "significant
OL,10,Finjuries" in the collision.
OL,12,FCoroner Ms Margaret Taylor formally
OL,13,Fopened the inquest into her death, and
OL,14,Fsaid: "Due to ongoing police
OL,15,Fenquiries, I am suspending the inquest
OL,16,Finto Mrs Gillian Livingstone's death.
OL,18,F"A decision upon resumption will be
OL,19,Fmade following the completion of
OL,20,Fpolice enquiries."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
